While researching [[Maruchan_Cup_Chili_Piquin_and_Shrimp]] I discovered
seafood flavor cup noodles are probably [Nissin's most popular cup noodle]
(https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000023.000135215.html), which was a very
surprising fact to learn. I kept this knowledge in a dusty corner of my brain
until today when I saw on the side of Nissin's Seafood cup noodles in H-Mart the
words "#1 in Japan". I guess it's true!

